{"data":[{"name":"79:1","price":"1 Par ceux qui arrachent les âmes[1539] violemment !","arabic":"وَٱلنَّٰزِعَٰتِ غَرۡقٗا","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5713,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"[1539] Des mécréants.","lang":"fr"},{"name":"79:2","price":"2 Par ceux qui recueillent les âmes[1540] délicatement !","arabic":"وَٱلنَّٰشِطَٰتِ نَشۡطٗا","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5714,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"[1540] Des croyants.","lang":"fr"},{"name":"79:3","price":"3 Par ceux qui glissent vélocement !","arabic":"وَٱلسَّٰبِحَٰتِ سَبۡحٗا","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5715,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"79:4","price":"4 Par ceux qui obéissent promptement !","arabic":"فَٱلسَّٰبِقَٰتِ سَبۡقٗا","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5716,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"79:5","price":"5 Par ceux qui exécutent les commandements[1541] !","arabic":"فَٱلۡمُدَبِّرَٰتِ أَمۡرٗا","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5717,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"[1541] Selon la majorité des exégètes, le pronom « ceux », dans les cinq versets précédents, désigne les anges.","lang":"fr"},{"name":"79:6","price":"6 Le Jour où la terre tremblera au premier soufflement[1542],","arabic":"يَوۡمَ تَرۡجُفُ ٱلرَّاجِفَةُ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5718,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"[1542] Dans la Corne, soufflement qui annoncera le Jour de la résurrection et foudroiera les hommes.","lang":"fr"},{"name":"79:7","price":"7 qui sera lui-même suivi d’un second soufflement[1543],","arabic":"تَتۡبَعُهَا ٱلرَّادِفَةُ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5719,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"[1543] Par lequel tous ressusciteront.","lang":"fr"},{"name":"79:8","price":"8 les cœurs de certains seront ce Jour-là bouleversés,","arabic":"قُلُوبٞ يَوۡمَئِذٖ وَاجِفَةٌ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5720,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"79:9","price":"9 tandis que leurs regards seront abaissés et humiliés.","arabic":"أَبۡصَٰرُهَا خَٰشِعَةٞ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5721,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"79:10","price":"10 Ceux-là mêmes qui disent : « Serons-nous ressuscités,","arabic":"يَقُولُونَ أَءِنَّا لَمَرۡدُودُونَ فِي ٱلۡحَافِرَةِ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5722,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"79:11","price":"11 alors que nous ne serons plus que des os désagrégés ? »","arabic":"أَءِذَا كُنَّا عِظَٰمٗا نَّخِرَةٗ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5723,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"79:12","price":"12 Ils ajoutent : « Ce serait un retour bien malheureux ! »","arabic":"قَالُواْ تِلۡكَ إِذٗا كَرَّةٌ خَاسِرَةٞ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5724,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"79:13","price":"13 Il suffira pourtant d’un seul et unique soufflement","arabic":"فَإِنَّمَا هِيَ زَجۡرَةٞ وَٰحِدَةٞ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5725,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"79:14","price":"14 pour que les morts se retrouvent à la surface de la terre.","arabic":"فَإِذَا هُم بِٱلسَّاهِرَةِ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5726,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"79:15","price":"15 L’histoire de Moïse t’est-elle parvenue ?","arabic":"هَلۡ أَتَىٰكَ حَدِيثُ مُوسَىٰٓ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5727,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"79:16","price":"16 Son Seigneur l’appela dans la vallée sainte de Touwâ, lui ordonnant :","arabic":"إِذۡ نَادَىٰهُ رَبُّهُۥ بِٱلۡوَادِ ٱلۡمُقَدَّسِ طُوًى","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5728,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"79:17","price":"17 « Rends-toi auprès de Pharaon qui se conduit en tyran.","arabic":"ٱذۡهَبۡ إِلَىٰ فِرۡعَوۡنَ إِنَّهُۥ طَغَىٰ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5729,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"79:18","price":"18 Dis-lui : “Ne veux-tu pas purifier ton âme de la souillure de l’impiété","arabic":"فَقُلۡ هَل لَّكَ إِلَىٰٓ أَن تَزَكَّىٰ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5730,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"79:19","price":"19 et que je te guide vers ton Seigneur afin que tu sois amené à Le redouter ?” »","arabic":"وَأَهۡدِيَكَ إِلَىٰ رَبِّكَ فَتَخۡشَىٰ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5731,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"79:20","price":"20 Moïse produisit des miracles prodigieux sous les yeux de Pharaon","arabic":"فَأَرَىٰهُ ٱلۡأٓيَةَ ٱلۡكُبۡرَىٰ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5732,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"79:21","price":"21 qui le traita de menteur, désobéissant ainsi à son Seigneur.","arabic":"فَكَذَّبَ وَعَصَىٰ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5733,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"79:22","price":"22 Se détournant de la foi et persistant dans le péché,","arabic":"ثُمَّ أَدۡبَرَ يَسۡعَىٰ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5734,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"79:23","price":"23 Pharaon rassembla ses sujets et proclama :","arabic":"فَحَشَرَ فَنَادَىٰ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5735,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"79:24","price":"24 « Je suis votre Dieu suprême ! »","arabic":"فَقَالَ أَنَا۠ رَبُّكُمُ ٱلۡأَعۡلَىٰ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5736,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"79:25","price":"25 Allah le châtiera donc dans l’au-delà comme Il le fit ici-bas.","arabic":"فَأَخَذَهُ ٱللَّهُ نَكَالَ ٱلۡأٓخِرَةِ وَٱلۡأُولَىٰٓ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5737,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"79:26","price":"26 Voilà bien un enseignement pour quiconque craint le Seigneur.","arabic":"إِنَّ فِي ذَٰلِكَ لَعِبۡرَةٗ لِّمَن يَخۡشَىٰٓ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5738,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"79:27","price":"27 Seriez-vous plus difficiles à créer[1544] que le ciel qu’Il a édifié, ","arabic":"ءَأَنتُمۡ أَشَدُّ خَلۡقًا أَمِ ٱلسَّمَآءُۚ بَنَىٰهَا","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5739,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"[1544] Après la mort, vous qui reniez la Résurrection.","lang":"fr"},{"name":"79:28","price":"28 dont Il a élevé la voûte et qu’Il a harmonieusement formé ?","arabic":"رَفَعَ سَمۡكَهَا فَسَوَّىٰهَا","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5740,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"79:29","price":"29 Il le plonge, la nuit, dans l’obscurité et l’inonde, le jour, de clarté.","arabic":"وَأَغۡطَشَ لَيۡلَهَا وَأَخۡرَجَ ضُحَىٰهَا","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5741,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"79:30","price":"30 Il a, après cela, étendu[1545] la terre,","arabic":"وَٱلۡأَرۡضَ بَعۡدَ ذَٰلِكَ دَحَىٰهَآ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5742,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"[1545] Ses bienfaits sur. En effet, selon certains exégètes, dont At-Tabari et Ibn Kathîr, le terme « étendu » est expliqué par les versets 31 et 32. ","lang":"fr"},{"name":"79:31","price":"31 faisant jaillir ses eaux et ses pâturages,","arabic":"أَخۡرَجَ مِنۡهَا مَآءَهَا وَمَرۡعَىٰهَا","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5743,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"79:32","price":"32 et y plantant solidement des montagnes,","arabic":"وَٱلۡجِبَالَ أَرۡسَىٰهَا","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5744,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"79:33","price":"33 bienfaits dont vous jouissez, vous et vos bestiaux.","arabic":"مَتَٰعٗا لَّكُمۡ وَلِأَنۡعَٰمِكُمۡ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5745,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"79:34","price":"34 Mais lorsque se produira le Cataclysme majeur,","arabic":"فَإِذَا جَآءَتِ ٱلطَّآمَّةُ ٱلۡكُبۡرَىٰ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5746,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"79:35","price":"35 le Jour où l’homme se souviendra de ses œuvres,","arabic":"يَوۡمَ يَتَذَكَّرُ ٱلۡإِنسَٰنُ مَا سَعَىٰ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5747,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"79:36","price":"36 et que le Brasier apparaîtra clairement à tous, ","arabic":"وَبُرِّزَتِ ٱلۡجَحِيمُ لِمَن يَرَىٰ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5748,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"79:37","price":"37 celui qui aura vécu dans la rébellion,","arabic":"فَأَمَّا مَن طَغَىٰ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5749,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"79:38","price":"38 préférant cette vie à celle de l’au-delà,","arabic":"وَءَاثَرَ ٱلۡحَيَوٰةَ ٱلدُّنۡيَا","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5750,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"79:39","price":"39 aura pour seul refuge la Fournaise.","arabic":"فَإِنَّ ٱلۡجَحِيمَ هِيَ ٱلۡمَأۡوَىٰ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5751,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"79:40","price":"40 Quant à celui qui, redoutant de comparaître devant son Seigneur, aura su dominer ses passions,","arabic":"وَأَمَّا مَنۡ خَافَ مَقَامَ رَبِّهِۦ وَنَهَى ٱلنَّفۡسَ عَنِ ٱلۡهَوَىٰ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5752,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"79:41","price":"41 il aura pour séjour éternel les jardins du Paradis.","arabic":"فَإِنَّ ٱلۡجَنَّةَ هِيَ ٱلۡمَأۡوَىٰ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5753,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"79:42","price":"42 Ils t’interrogent sur l’Heure, sur le jour de son avènement.","arabic":"يَسۡـَٔلُونَكَ عَنِ ٱلسَّاعَةِ أَيَّانَ مُرۡسَىٰهَا","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5754,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"79:43","price":"43 Comment pourrais-tu, toi, les informer de cet événement ","arabic":"فِيمَ أَنتَ مِن ذِكۡرَىٰهَآ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5755,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"79:44","price":"44 qui relève de la science de ton Seigneur uniquement ?","arabic":"إِلَىٰ رَبِّكَ مُنتَهَىٰهَآ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5756,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"79:45","price":"45 Tu es simplement chargé d’avertir ceux qui en redoutent l’avènement.","arabic":"إِنَّمَآ أَنتَ مُنذِرُ مَن يَخۡشَىٰهَا","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5757,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"79:46","price":"46 Le Jour où ils en seront témoins, il leur semblera n’être restés sur terre que l’espace d’une soirée ou d’une matinée.","arabic":"كَأَنَّهُمۡ يَوۡمَ يَرَوۡنَهَا لَمۡ يَلۡبَثُوٓاْ إِلَّا عَشِيَّةً أَوۡ ضُحَىٰهَا","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5758,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"}],"chapter":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at","Chapter An-Nazi'at","Nazi'at","Surah Nazi'at","Chapter Nazi'at","An Nazi'at","Surah An Nazi'at","Chapter An Nazi'at","Surah 79","Chapter 79","Those Who Pull Out","النازعات"]}